    "user": "U061HDV96",
    "text": "Seems like quite a simple question which I answered before. But here it goes:\nIs the data you get applied only on 1 fragment or 1 activity?\nPut it in that activity.\nElse if the data you get is applied to multiple fragments, put it in the parent activity.",
    "ts": "1438885901.001583",
    "id": "06de6166",
    "thread": [
      {
        "position": "null",
        "number": 0
      }
    ],
    "label": [
      {
        "type": "null",
        "position": "null"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "user": "U0546QERR",
    "text": "if the data is used in multiple places i’d probably make a model/interactor and use that in the fragments",
